<h1>Privacy Policy</h1>

<p>At <strong>Global Fresh News</strong>, your privacy is important to us.</p>

<h3>1. Information We Collect</h3>
<p>We may collect personal information such as your name and email when you leave comments or contact us.</p>

<h3>2. How We Use Your Information</h3>
<p>Your information is used to improve user experience, respond to inquiries, and manage content on our platform.</p>

<h3>3. Cookies</h3>
<p>We use cookies to enhance your experience, analyze traffic,
and serve personalized ads.</p>

<h3>4. Third-Party Services</h3>
<p>We may use third-party tools (like analytics or ads) that collect data in accordance with their policies.</p>

<h3>5. Data Protection</h3>
<p>We take reasonable steps to protect your data but cannot guarantee absolute security.</p>

<h3>6. Changes</h3>
<p>We may update this Privacy Policy at any time.</p>

<p><strong>Last updated:</strong> 2026</p>


